A protectedProcedure query that returns all items for the current user with status BAD, OLD, or FRESH, ordered BAD first then OLD then FRESH. Includes itemTypes with id, name, and suggested_life_span_seconds so the client can compute getDaysUntilExpiration without a second round-trip. The client-side useAtRiskReview hook does the final filter to exclude FRESH items with more than 3 days remaining (using the existing getDaysUntilExpiration utility in src/utils/expiration.ts).

  getAtRiskItems: protectedProcedure
    .query(async ({ ctx }) => {
