- The dynamic import pattern for NotificationService matches exactly what check-expiring-items.ts does — keep it consistent.
- The notification body format intentionally mirrors the existing ITEM_EXPIRING format for familiarity.
- The 'AT_RISK_REVIEW' type in push data.type is used by the service worker (broccoli-dashboard-a2b) to decide the deep-link URL.

